main event: Two circular objects were observed in the sky over Kirksville, Missouri on May 23, 1962.
interesting points: The objects were observed for 2-3 minutes,One object seemed to change shape and flash lights or change color,The objects moved erratically and then disappeared from sight, The witnesses were school children and their reliability is unknown due to age, This sighting could not be satisfactorily identified as aircraft.
sighted object: two circular objects in the sky
